workflow.name: Creating SEO-optimized blogs for WordPress using specific tools
workflow.description:
# ‚úçÔ∏è AI-Powered High-Quality Blog Automation  
Automate **SEO-optimized blog creation, publishing, and internal linking** ‚Äî designed for Lovable.dev or seamless WordPress integration.  
**Proven to boost impressions by +15% weekly** on real websites.
![image.png](fileId:2326)
üìå **Example:** [AI Applications in Real Estate Playbook](https://taskmorphr.com/blog/ai-applications-in-real-estate-playbook) ‚Äî fully generated, optimized, and published with this automation.

---

## üöÄ What This Workflow Does
- **Bring Your Own Keywords**  
  You provide the keyword list ‚Äî the workflow applies a **scoring formula** to rank them by relevance and competition for maximum SEO impact.

- **Keyword Scoring & Logging**  
  Scores primary and secondary keywords, logs them in **PostgreSQL**, and prevents reuse until strategically relevant.

- **Deep Research & Blog Planning**  
  Uses **Perplexity AI** and other AI models to outline, plan, and enrich each article with authoritative external sources.

- **SEO-Optimized Redaction**  
  Writes **multi-part, long-form blogs** with integrated **internal links** (to your existing content) and **external links** to reputable sites.

- **Image Generation & Selection**  
  Creates or selects high-quality header and in-article images, optimized for your topic.

- **Full Blog Infrastructure**  
  - Internal & external linking logic  
  - Blog card + metadata updates  
  - Sitemap updates & Google indexing submission  
  - Post logging for future reference

- **Publishing Flexibility**  
  - Direct GitHub commits for **Lovable.dev**  
  - WordPress-ready export  
  - Optional Slack approval before publishing

---

## üîó Integrated Services
- **PostgreSQL** ‚Äì Keyword & content database  
- **Perplexity AI** ‚Äì Research & planning  
- **OpenAI / OpenRouter Models** ‚Äì Multi-part blog writing  
- **Lovable.dev / GitHub** ‚Äì Direct publishing  
- **WordPress-ready JSON output** ‚Äì Easy CMS import  
- **Slack** ‚Äì Approval workflow before going live

---

## üíº What You Get
- **Detailed Setup Guide**  
- **Workflow Description**

---

## üì• Perfect For
- Website owners wanting **consistent SEO growth**  
- Agencies handling multiple client sites  
- Marketers running content-heavy campaigns  
- Lovable.dev or WordPress users who want **hands-off publishing**

---

## üí° Why You‚Äôll Love It
This is more than a blog writer ‚Äî it‚Äôs **a complete content infrastructure**. From keyword prioritization to publishing and indexing, it keeps your site growing in reach and authority while you focus on your business.

data.details: The Code node allows you to execute JavaScript in your workflow.

The Filter node can be used to filter items based on a condition. If the condition is met, the item will be passed on to the next node. If the condition is not met, the item will be omitted. Conditions can be combined together by AND(meet all conditions), or OR(meet at least one condition).
